## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **cabergoline (Dostinex) 1996** = first-line + DA agonist + 만성 표준 dopamine D2 long-acting twice-weekly oral. quantum-VQE 의 D2 long residence pocket fit.
2. **bromocriptine (Parlodel) 1980s** = first DA agonist + 만성 historical + 만성 임신 안전 paradigm. cabergoline 으로 second-line 으로 밀렸으나 임신 시 first 으로 회귀.
3. **pergolide (Permax) withdrawn 2007** = valvular heart disease (5-HT2B agonism) — DA agonist class warning. cabergoline >3mg/wk echocardiography monitoring 의 근거.
4. **quinagolide (Norprolac)** = third DA agonist EU/한국 승인 — US 미승인. selective D2 → cabergoline 대체 한정.
5. **transsphenoidal surgery (TSS) + stereotactic radiosurgery (SRS) + fractionated RT** = second/third-line — macroprolactinoma + cabergoline-resistant + refractory. 1차 surgical 사용 예외 (대부분 medical 1L) 가 다른 pituitary adenoma 와 다른 점.
6. **temozolomide off-label atypical/refractory prolactinoma** (cross-glioma_glioblastoma_specific) = MGMT methylation status 가 response predictor. quantum-VQE 의 DNA alkylation pocket cross-fit.
7. **antipsychotic-induced hyperprolactinemia** (aripiprazole D2 partial agonist + olanzapine — cross-psychiatric) = 임상 hyperprolactinemia 의 가장 흔한 secondary cause. management framework: switch to aripiprazole 또는 quetiapine.
8. **dopamine D2 + D3 + D4 receptor cross-selectivity** = next-gen DA agonist 의 핵심. cardiac valve 안전 (5-HT2B avoidance) + dyskinesia 감소 (D3/D4 selectivity).
9. **K-prolactinoma 임상 framework** + 식약처 + 산정특례 + 한국 만성 hyperprolactinemia 진료 paradigm = K-pharma cross-link essential.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, prolactinoma 임상 의미 한정.

